casebody.data:
No. 109,

Orig.

Oklahoma et al. v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 956.]

Motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $71,790.81 for the period February 1 through November 8, 1990, one-third to be paid by each party.
